Using emacs or mousepad , type program name with .cpp extension

We can use ctrl+alt+t , to open terminal directly

If using emacs first catch the dir , then type emacs in terminal

After typing the program, enter 
        Esc + X
        
        Then type compile
        Compile using g++ program_name.cpp
        
        Again press Esc + X
        Type shell for O/P of program
        Run using ./a.out
